description: USE WHEN showing global modal loaders, opening maps, decoding bundle JSON to models, fetching link previews, logging errors, using GlobalKey layout, rotating Image widgets, MIME checks on File, or HTTP status coloring. Prefer kartal utilities and extensions.
globs:
  - "**/*.dart"
alwaysApply: false
