# Kartal utilities & misc extensions

| Topic | API |
|-------|-----|
| Loader | `context.popupManager.showLoader()` / `hideLoader({id})` — root `Navigator` |
| Maps | `MapsUtility.openAppleMapsWithQuery`, `openGoogleMapsWithQuery`, `openGoogleWebMapsWithQuery` |
| Assets | `BundleDecoder(path).crackBundle<T,R>(model:)` with `IAssetModel<T>` |
| Link preview | `CustomLinkPreview.getLinkPreviewData(url)` |
| Log | `CustomLogger.showError<T>(error)` |
| HTTP color | `statusCode.ext.httpStatus` / `httpStatusColor`; `HttpResult.fromStatusCode` |
| Device | `DeviceUtility.instance` |
| Key | `globalKey.ext.{rendererBox,offset,height,scrollToWidget}` |
| Image | `image.ext.{rightRotation,upRotation,bottomRotation,leftRotation}` |
| Bool | `flag.ext.isSuccess` / `isFail` |
| Color | `color.ext.randomColor`, `withOpacity` |
| Date | `dateTime.ext.differenceTime(...)` |
| File | `file.ext.fileType`, `isImageFile`, … |

Do not fight declarative routers with `context.route.*` without checking project navigation architecture.
